            <p><span class="bold">{%trans "Water" %}</span> – {%trans "the impact of your Actions on water use, contaminant levels and pollution" %}</p>
            <p><span class="bold">{%trans "Species" %}</span> – {%trans "the impact of your Actions on the ecosystems and populations of animals" %}</p>
